 LW, Chen CH. Spontaneous rupture of an ovarian artery aneurysm: case report and review of the literature. <em>Gynecol Obstet Invest</em> 2009;68(2): 104–107.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1159/000220603">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19478526/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Spontaneous+rupture+of+an+ovarian+artery+aneurysm%3A+case+report+and+review+of+the+literature&amp;author=LW+Chao&amp;author=CH+Chen&amp;publication_year=2009&amp;journal=Gynecol+Obstet+Invest&amp;pages=104-107&amp;doi=10.1159%2F000220603&amp;pmid=19478526">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">73.</div><div id="r73" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Hollis HW, Luethke JM, Yakes WF, Beitler AL. Percutaneous embolization of an internal iliac artery aneurysm: technical considerations and literature review. <em>J Vasc Interv Radiol</em> 1994;5(3):449–451.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/S1051-0443(94)71526-8">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8054744/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Percutaneous+embolization+of+an+internal+iliac+artery+aneurysm%3A+technical+considerations+and+literature+review&amp;author=HW+Hollis&amp;author=JM+Luethke&amp;author=WF+Yakes&amp;author=AL+Beitler&amp;publication_year=1994&amp;journal=J+Vasc+Interv+Radiol&amp;pages=449-451&amp;doi=10.1016%2FS1051-0443%2894%2971526-8&amp;pmid=8054744">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">74.</div><div id="r74" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citati