5si055503">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16227490/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Pseudoaneurysms+and+the+role+of+minimally+invasive+techniques+in+their+management&amp;author=NE+Saad&amp;author=WE+Saad&amp;author=MG+Davies&amp;author=DL+Waldman&amp;author=PJ+Fultz&amp;author=DJ+Rubens&amp;publication_year=2005&amp;journal=RadioGraphics&amp;pages=S173-S189&amp;doi=10.1148%2Frg.25si055503&amp;pmid=16227490">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></section></div><div class="core-collateral" role="dialog" aria-modal="true"><div id="core-collateral-info" data-active-pane="false"><header><h2><i class="icon-info" aria-hidden="true"></i>Information &amp; Authors</h2></header><section id="tab-information" role="tabpanel"><h3>Information</h3><section class="core-self-citation"><h4>Published In</h4><div class="core-journal-presentation">



        
